<h3 class=3D"wp-block-heading">Controller Work</h3>



<div style=3D"height:20px" aria-hidden=3D"true" class=3D"wp-block-spacer"><=
/div>



<p>NASA Glenn develops in-house Stirling controllers for dynamic space powe=
r generation systems, including radioisotope power systems (RPS) and fissio=
n surface power (FSP). Multiple breadboard hardware units are built to supp=
ort rapid design iteration, enabling timely development of robust flight-re=
ady controllers.</p>



<p>NASA also collaborates with external partners to deliver Stirling contro=
ller technologies for a range of projects supporting both NASA and the U.S.=
 Department of Defense. </p>


